<p>Happy April Fools Day/Easter everybody! I created this in a day by sheer force of will and disgusting writing. Thank you to MaliceAforethought for giving me the idea for the theoretically infinite Samuel Lloyds.</p>
<p>The black image was created by me in MS Paint, the shrugging image is from Wikimedia Commons and is licensed for public use.</p>
<p>Special thanks to Jabyrwock and shaggydredlocks for critting this hot garbage.</p>
<p>If you like this style of writing, I wrote my author page in the same style: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-s-mann-s-personnel-file">http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-s-mann-s-personnel-file</a></p>
<p>Thank you all for reading!</p>
<p>EDIT: A little before the year anniversary of V1L3-J being posted, I posted its spiritual successor, <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-pu1p-j">SCP-PU1P-J!</a> This one is less sexual, yet somehow even more absurd.</p>

